# Pin line endings for the deploy bundle so manifest.json's md5 checksums stay
# valid across platforms and CI (verified by scripts/check_calibrate_manifest.sh).
# All text sources are already LF; this keeps them LF regardless of a contributor's
# core.autocrlf. Binaries are marked so git never touches them.
*.R    text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.png  binary
